    <div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn">
           <p><pb n="1r"/>
             <lb n="1"/><g type="spiral">.</g>svasti samasta-bhuvanā<choice><orig>s</orig><reg>ś</reg></choice>raya srī-<choice><orig>prituvi</orig><reg>pr̥thvī</reg></choice>
                 -vallabhaṁ mahārājādhirāja parame
             <lb n="2" break="no"/>śvara-parama-bhaṭṭāra-satyā<choice><orig>s</orig><reg>ś</reg></choice>raya-kuḷa-tiḷakaṁ cāḷukyābharaṇaṁ
             <lb n="3"/>śrīmatr<choice><orig>i</orig><reg>ai</reg></choice><orig>i</orig>lōkyamalladēvara rājyadalu</p>
           <p><choice><orig>s</orig><reg>ś</reg></choice>aka <choice><orig>variṣa</orig><reg></reg>varṣa</choice> 897 neya yu
             <lb n="4" break="no"/>va saṁvatsarada bhādrapadad’ <choice><orig>amavāse</orig><reg>amāvāsye</reg></choice> Ādityavāra byatipāta sūrya
             <lb n="5" break="no"/>grahaṇadandu</p>
           <p>śrīmadaṁ kuliyarasar piriya būtayya gaḍaṁ
               <lb n="6" break="no"/>ba kaḍaṁbē<choice><orig>s</orig><reg>ś</reg></choice>varamaṁ māḍsi sivarāsi-jīyara kālaṁ karcci bi
               <lb n="7" break="no"/>ṭṭa dharmmaṁ</p>
           <p>taḷagada dharmma-gēri kaḍaṁbēsvara dēvargge yu
               <pb n="1v"/>
               <lb n="8"/><gap reason="illegible" unit="character" quantity="1"/>jamaḷasa kaṇnasa baddhagivāḷu sātēvāḷu Ini nityaṁ
               <lb n="9"/>dēvas<choice><sic>t</sic><corr>v</corr></choice>aṁ nandā-dīvigege sōḍargge haradara k<choice><orig>e</orig><reg>ē</reg></choice>riyalu pa
               <lb n="10" break="no"/>tu gadyāṇaṁ teṁkaṇa kēriyal aydu gadyāṇa</p> 
            <p>Inidhellamaṁ
               <lb n="11"/><choice><orig>ki</orig><reg>ke</reg></choice>ḍisidavargge kurukṣētrada banārāsiyalu sāsira kavile
               <lb n="12" break="no"/>yan aḷida dōṣaṁ <supplied reason="lost">ī</supplied> dharmmavaṁ aḻidavriṁge <g type="danda">.</g></p>
           <p><g type="spiral">.</g><g type="danda">.</g>svasti <choice><sic>kō</sic><corr>ma</corr></choice>
               <lb n="13" break="no"/>lyāṇaṁ kaḍaṁbē<supplied reason="lost">śva</supplied>ra dēvara kāsu pattege siraṁjiyāt· <g type="spiral"></g></p>
